entry.value: Plaster Cast of a Womans Torso
Plaster Cast of a Womans Torso 1
Letter from Vincent van Gogh to Theo van Gogh with sketches of Head of a Woman and Head of a Woman
which he painted a number of times
He would use this technique more than once in his later work
